211
00:12:22,050 --> 00:12:25,320
Pesas mucho, no puedo respirar.

212
00:12:27,030 --> 00:12:28,010
Sal de arriba mío.

213
00:12:28,990 --> 00:12:32,330
Esto no es judo.

214
00:12:32,330 --> 00:12:37,020
